House Resolution 637
By: Representatives Scott of the 76th, Schofield of the 63rd, and Davis of the 87th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Mr. Daniel Kiptoo Bargoria on his outstanding public service;
2 and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Mr. Daniel Kiptoo Bargoria has significantly impacted Kenya's energy sector
4 as the Director General of the Energy and Petroleum Regulatory Authority (EPRA) since
5 December 14, 2020; and
6 WHEREAS, in his current role as Director General of the Energy and Petroleum Regulatory
7 Authority (EPRA), Mr. Bargoria regulates Kenya's electricity and petroleum sectors,
8 ensuring efficient and sustainable operations across the entire value chain; and
9 WHEREAS, Mr. Bargoria's leadership is marked by several notable achievements, including
10 as chairman of the Government's First Oil Committee, where he oversaw the delivery of
11 Kenya's first oil, a historic milestone positioning Kenya as a new player in the global oil
12 market; and
13 WHEREAS, Mr. Bargoria's contributions to Kenya's energy legislation are significant, as he
14 was instrumental in drafting the Kenyan Energy Act (2019) and Petroleum Act (2019), which
