18 remarkable and distinguished individual be appropriately recognized.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body recognize and commend Mr. Daniel Kiptoo Bargoria for his
21 efficient, effective, unselfish, and dedicated public service to Kenya and extend the most
22 sincere best wishes for continued health and happiness.
